{
  "id": "69f58a5507148d6104a04f02",
  "title": "自ら手を動かしたほうが強い",
  "created": 1777699415,
  "updated": 1777699415,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f58a5507148d6104a04f02",
      "text": "自ら手を動かしたほうが強い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f1",
      "text": "from [2026/04/16]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f2",
      "text": "  [自ら手を動かしたほうが強い]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f3",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f4",
      "text": "\t[自ら手を動かしたほうが強い]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f5",
      "text": "\t似たような言葉が色々思い浮かぶ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f6",
      "text": " \t論より証拠",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f7",
      "text": " \t口より手を動かせ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f8",
      "text": " 実物を見られるのが良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1f9",
      "text": " \t大変そう、要らなさそう、要りそう、役に立ちそう、邪魔なんじゃないか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1fa",
      "text": " \t→ 取り敢えず作ったからまず見よ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1fb",
      "text": " \t\t大変だった。私は要らない。私は要る。こう使うと役に立つ。案の定邪魔だった。私は面白かった。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1fc",
      "text": "\t政治的な強さがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1fd",
      "text": "\t\t要ると思うけど手間がかかるのを想像するとちょっと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1fe",
      "text": "\t\t\t→もうやったから手間0になったよ。後は要るか要らないか実物見て",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a1ff",
      "text": "\t\t要らないと思っていたが、作った後で「これやっぱりあると面白い」と気づくことがある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58a550000000000c6a200",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699415,
      "updated": 1777699415
    }
  ]
}